#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn56.60"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.60:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.60:0.2"
msgid "6. Abhisamayavagga "
msgstr "6. Comprehension "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.60:0.3"
msgid "60. Dutiyapabbatūpamasutta "
msgstr "60. A Mountain (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.465, sc1
msgctxt "sn56.60:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, himavā pabbatarājā parikkhayaṃ pariyādānaṃ gaccheyya, ṭhapetvā satta sāsapamattiyo pāsāṇasakkharā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, suppose the Himalayas, the king of mountains, was worn away and eroded except for seven pebbles the size of mustard seeds. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.60:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn56.60:1.3"
msgid "katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ—yaṃ vā himavato pabbatarājassa parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādinnaṃ, yā vā satta sāsapamattiyo pāsāṇasakkharā avasiṭṭhā”ti? "
msgstr "Which is more: the portion of the Himalayas, the king of mountains, that has been worn away and eroded, or the seven pebbles the size of mustard seeds that are left?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.60:1.4"
msgid "“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ himavato pabbatarājassa yadidaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādinnaṃ; appamattikā satta sāsapamattiyo pāsāṇasakkharā avasiṭṭhā. "
msgstr "“Sir, the portion of the Himalayas, the king of mountains, that has been worn away and eroded is certainly more. The seven pebbles the size of mustard seeds are tiny. "

msgctxt "sn56.60:1.5"
msgid "Saṅkhampi na upenti, upanidhampi na upenti, kalabhāgampi na upenti himavato pabbatarājassa parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādinnaṃ upanidhāya satta sāsapamattiyo pāsāṇasakkharā avasiṭṭhā”ti. "
msgstr "Compared to the Himalayas, they can’t be reckoned or compared, they’re not even a fraction.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.60:1.6"
msgid "“Evameva kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa diṭṭhisampannassa puggalassa abhisametāvino etadeva bahutaraṃ dukkhaṃ yadidaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādinnaṃ; appamattakaṃ avasiṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr "“In the same way, for a person with comprehension, a noble disciple accomplished in view, the suffering that’s over and done with is more, what’s left is tiny. "

msgctxt "sn56.60:1.7"
msgid "Saṅkhampi na upeti, upanidhampi na upeti, kalabhāgampi na upeti, purimaṃ dukkhakkhandhaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādinnaṃ upanidhāya yadidaṃ sattakkhattuparamatā; "
msgstr "Compared to the mass of suffering in the past that’s over and done with, it can’t be reckoned or compared, it’s not even a fraction, since there are at most seven more lives. "

msgctxt "sn56.60:1.8"
msgid "yo ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. "
msgstr "Such a person truly understands about suffering, its origin, its cessation, and the path. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn56.60:2.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti. "
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.60:2.2"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.60:2.3"
msgid "Abhisamayavaggo chaṭṭho. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn56.60:3.1"
msgid "Nakhasikhā pokkharaṇī, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.60:3.2"
msgid "sambhejja apare duve; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.60:3.3"
msgid "Pathavī dve samuddā dve, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.60:3.4"
msgid "dvemā ca pabbatūpamāti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
